content:
Printworks（印刷厂）是位于伦敦南部的电子音乐俱乐部和活动场所，2020年DJ Mag百大俱乐部排名第五位。Printworks于2017年开业，开幕活动邀请了Seth Troxler、The Martinez Brothers和Loco Dice等艺术家表演。原址为Harmsworth Quays印刷厂，曾负责Daily Mail（每日邮报）和Evening Standard（标准晚报）的印刷，故亦因此得名。原址遗留的部分设施和室内结构、设计，为Printwork营造了浓郁的工业氛围。

 

Printworks总规模可以容纳达到5000人，目前有两个表演间（Press Hall和Darkroom），新的空间Inkwells将与2021年开放
contentEn: Printworks is a nightclub and events venue in Rotherhithe, South London. It is located in the former Harmsworth Quays printing plant, which printed newspapers including the Daily Mail and Evening Standard until 2012.Some features of the printing plant have been retained including the van loading dock and metal stairs, creating an industrial feel in the club. The club has an overall capacity of 5,000 people for DJ events across two performance rooms (the Press. Halls and the Darkroom).
